=== Integer Operations ===
2^10:      1024
divMod:    (3, 2)

=== Bitwise ===
and 0xF0 0x0F: 0
or  0xF0 0x0F: 255
xor 0xFF 0x0F: 240
shiftL 1 8:    256
popCount 255:  8

=== Trigonometry ===
sin(pi/6):  0.5000010603626028
cos(pi/3):  0.49999787927254574
atan2(1,1): 0.7853981633974483

=== Exponentials & Logs ===
exp(1):   2.718281828459045
log(e):   0.999999327347282
log2(8):  3
log10(1000): 3
sqrt(2):  1.4142135623730951
cbrt(27): 3

=== Special values ===
isNaN(0/0):   True
isInfinite:   True
